---
title: Mushroom and Spinach Flatbread with Fresh Mozzarella, Garlic, and Parmesan
description: Cooking mushrooms and onions will bring everyone in your house around the stove. The smell is irresistible! Paired with garlicky spinach and fresh mozzarella, these toppings guarantee an epic pizza night.
